<i>noun</i>: 석면 [성면] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>석면 [성면]</dt><br>
<dd>asbestos</dd><br>
<dd>산성이나 염기성에 강하고 열과 전기가 잘 통하지 않아 불과 열, 전류 등을 막는 재료로 쓰이는 광물.</dd><br>
<dd>A mineral that is highly resistant to acidity and alkalinity and cannot transmit heat and electricity properly so that it is used as a material to resist fire, heat, electricity, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>